
Version 0.2.0
=============

02/24/05

* Added the ability to use keyboard keys to trigger scrolling instead of mouse
  buttons. See option "-k".
* Added a toggle mode, where the key/button toggles scroll mode (press once to
  enable scrolling, press again to disable). See option "-T".


Version 0.1.0
=============

02/21/05

* Initial release
